title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Vegetable, Fruit, Nuts, Plant Parts Prepared
description: Imports Intra Eu - Vegetable, Fruit, Nuts, Plant Parts Prepared in the United Kingdom increased to 254.71 GBP Million in September from 251.01 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Vegetable, Fruit, Nuts, Plant P in the United Kingdom averaged 130.97 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 285.44 GBP Million in May of 2022 and a record low of 37.91 GBP Million in February of 2022.
